en.codex: The Latron Wraith is a powerful variation of the standard, semi-automatic rifle that features unique styling.
en.description: The Latron Wraith is the Wraith version of the Latron semi-automatic rifle, which was featured as a reward for players who extracted 3000 Cryotic in a single mission during Operation Cryotic Front and can be found as an Invasion reward.

ru.description: Латрон Призрак - это более мощная версия стандартной, полуавтоматической винтовки, которая имеет уникальный дизайн.
